    "title": "Mid-Level Fleet Manager at Gateway Distriparks",
    "description": "Join the Gateway Distriparks family as a Fleet Manager in Coimbatore. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Gateway Distriparks:\nGateway Distriparks is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gateway Distriparks!",
